-1 SLAYERS SPELLS~
This group of spells, taken from the Slayers anime, are used
to inflict massive amounts of damage and destruction to others.
They are high level spells for the mage class only:

doragu sureibu    invokes a powerful shot of negative energy
ra tiruto         bends a beam of astral energy toward an opponent
raguna bureedo    creates a wieldable dagger of pure negative energy
~

-1 DORAGU SUREIBU~
Syntax:  cast 'doragu sureibu' <target>


Darkness from twilight
Crimson from blood that flows
Buried in the flow of time
In Thy great name,I pledge myself to darkness!
Those who oppose us shall be destroyed by the 
power you and I possess!
DRAGU SLAVE!!

By calling on the Lord of Darkness, this spell causes an extraordinary
amount of negative energy to be shot from the caster to the opponent.
It contains enoughs power to destroy entire cities.
~

-1 RA TIRUTO~
Syntax: cast 'ra tiruto'  <target>


The strongest spirit magic spell which envelops a target in blue-white
light. This spell can only be used against a single target --
and only those that have spirits -- but its effect is absolute.
The blue-white flame is said to destroy even a pure Demon destroy
with a single shot.
~

-1 RAGUNA BUREEDO~
Syntax: cast 'raguna bureedo'


The Laguna Blade, created by calling on the powers of the Lord of
Nightmares, creates a dagger of pure negative energy.  Because of it's
powerful nature, it can only be held for a limited amount of time before
it crumbles to dust.
~

