The function '`&dtoggle``' was added so that you could toggle descriptions
of players and mobiles. This way, if you're not interested in having to
scroll past lines of useless or offensive text, `&dtoggle`` is the way to go.
It saves when you exit so you'll have to type it again to view descriptions.

Change added on 8/26/2000 by Vorlin.
