This allows Saiyans to collect their will into the palms of their
hands and then suddenly release it on their oppenent causing injury.
The blast generated is dependant upon ones level. The more the level
the more damage this technique can deal. Using this technique also
reduces ones movement. This move cannot be performed if the user is
near death or out of movement.
